        <dt>Helpful Extensions</dt>
        <dd>Browse <a href="/download/extensions/field-types/">field type extensions</a> · Browse <a href="/download/extensions/text-formatters/">text formatter extensions</a></dd>
    </dl>
    <h4>Managing Content</h4>
    <p><strong>Resources for:</strong> creating and managing entries.</p>
    <dl class="resource-list">
